@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ugaqfn(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = ((v1 + wp.exp(v0 + 0.43)) - v2)
    v0 = ((v2 / 0.17) - v2)
    v1 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.98 * v2 + 0.07)) + 0.20)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(tmp + 0.89)) * v2)
    tmp = (wp.sin(0.11) / tmp)
    tmp = tmp
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(0.92))
    v2 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.25 - v0 + 0.85)) - wp.exp((tmp + 0.75 + v2 + 0.88)))
    data[tid] = v0
